{"tid":1606143,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我哋要做返次主動，10.1絕對唔可以再空手而回","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T16:42:25.000Z","uid":270871,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb959c08c8d1c2c5d44d6491b9419e96ba2c686","tid":1606143,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"持續嘅勇武抗爭有練兵效果<br />\n愈嚟愈多手足齊gear同愈行愈前<br />\n但係最近大多數行動都係被迫勇武，俾狗牽住走<br />\n<br />\n6.21圍警總、7.1佔立法會、7.21圍中聯辦、8.24觀塘燈柱<br />\n呢啲我哋都係事前諗定一啲有<span style=\"color: red;\">重大政治意義</span>嘅目標嚟打<br />\n目標明確、主動出擊<br />\n但係最近係唔知因為留力定習得性無助定輸咗俾白色恐怖<br />\n做乜都話危險、走唔到<br />\n避狗、走佬似乎做咗大家嘅最優先考慮<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">行動缺乏計劃同政治意圖</span>，然後美其名撚狗<br />\n反而黑警嘅行動仲多變過我哋<br />\n以前好多人都話六四集會七一遊行行禮如儀，冇策略冇變化冇目標<br />\n我唔希望勇武抗爭都落得呢個地步<br />\n<br />\n我哋要重奪主導權<br />\n麻煩大家出發前睇熟當區地圖<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背熟所有重要建築物同地標</span><br />\n心入面諗定自己想攻啲咩，攻唔到有咩後備方案<br />\n然後喺現場提出<br />\n<br />\n勝利係我哋唯一嘅生路<br />\n一輸我哋失去嘅將會係整個民族<br />\n我哋嘅義士、我哋嘅國歌、我哋嘅精神、我哋以血淚換嚟嘅民族意識<br />\n所有嘢都會付之一炬<br />\n我唔想見到香港喺幾十年後只係淪為一個悲劇故事<br />\n我哋唯有重拾六七月嘅激情，背水一戰嘅悲壯<br />\n好似7.21咁突破狗嘅防線嚟達成自己嘅目標重奪主導<br />\n<br />\n理想係各區都攻佔一啲重要建築物／象徵性地標<br />\n然後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">各區一齊讀光復香港宣言</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9a6c6f36ac9404f5ddcf2f48ab3ded3d1b074bc8","tid":1606143,"uid":270237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日出去前睇左先</span></span></span><br />\n來自CSD職員既提醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你班勇武手足,同我聽住,有部份前線手足認識我地,之前幾場戰役我地合作過,最初有人以為我地係鬼,詳細唔多講,我地係一班受過專業防暴訓練懲教署職員,之前已經係現場教過大家,如何組織防線同攻擊防暴,之前都有唔少進步,但今日我地冇出現,你地表現太差,中要咁多比人拉,我好心痛..<br />\n我地人手有限,身份問題,冇可能次次出現,我係度比些少資訊大家,希望大家務必share同發輝得好D<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.速龍都係人,佢地咩住咁重裝備同蒙面先至令信心大增,但大家留意下佢地人手一定唔夠手足多,只要大家穩固防線,只要佢地一跑出嚟,手足唔走向前攻,先用人火同磚頭攻,再快速向前推進, 趁機會足幾個差人抬去自己方向,呢個時候繼續用磚頭攻擊,同時向差人方向口射洗潔精地下,務別令佢地仆街,最重要立即除佢哋面具,之後私了..佢地以後就會驚..</span></span><br />\n2.佩槍唔係向上蚊,而係向內45度角向前推,大家明點做😁<br />\n3.如果執到警槍,同佢地玩過遊戲,逐粒子彈唔小心跌落坑渠,洗手間,包保玩殘佢地...<br />\n4.咁黑仔有狗用槍指你,可行情況試下用1秒用長竹,或雨傘打佢手同向上..<br />\n5如果打狗,唔該搵手足集中打腳,上半身有盾牌你打係冇用,要傷腳同關節先有足,以上除左增強攻擊同防護能力之外,就係要令到狗驚,你要記住佢地都係人,唔係超人...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.哨兵必須去遠少少,手足唔好集足一個地方,必須快速移動,不停向唔同地方攻擊,切斷差人增援,攻擊完立即走人,玩殘班狗..</span></span><br />\n7.盡量引班狗去橋下,用高空方式攻擊..<br />\n最後10.1見,大家努力<br />\n一班CSD職員上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HUQpWc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HUQpWc.jpg&h=14466c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UdMn0uy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUdMn0uy.jpg&h=f5ea24d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87ad2a74353763e6f6513ba327d87c017a708418","tid":1606143,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bfed23dab3c8214c54e5a40b1c09a120aa09ec","tid":1606143,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dGVTmzV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGVTmzV.jpg&h=c9cd4e99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e9c98f5063f321a4874a270d686d9119f6dafe1","tid":1606143,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:24:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fd2c81b952fdd34f6a53d5432f15405304da57e","tid":1606143,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d41d22a8970a69e82a7ebb7ed9130ea4144ecb3","tid":1606143,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zhwF7kd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzhwF7kd.jpg&h=5781479b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v40Ly0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv40Ly0d.jpg&h=3864b67f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">原po在此：<br />\n【重要行動/文宣】十一光復香港宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595334</a></span>"},{"pid":"a0d902abaef303f1e8e5bfbe8ddbdda32631bd26","tid":1606143,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a19436cfd5f1814a82a676a3a09b92ed5516b3a","tid":1606143,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"做獵人定獵物 自己揀"},{"pid":"a5da73905be1b91557afc4ee6e7998e78bad4cc4","tid":1606143,"uid":243834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:52:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0821d9f2d77012d2b52c7429c26e4522607c868b","tid":1606143,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"df9ca989fa4e7575dec4e4cacd1a5a0685ca073c","tid":1606143,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:56:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4699bd118e0bce3da55a42021578facb174cead1","tid":1606143,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:13:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e89b067385458ab04472398b5ff4ab3ce690c3d4","tid":1606143,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"大家聽日要有目標！唔好再賽跑啦！記得保護自己保護手足<br />\n<br />\n《終極軍師》勇武請入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605991\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605991</a>"},{"pid":"79bc02a130f8700c677e52e8f4bdd491de878e10","tid":1606143,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe63a3990808da504db65839565ce740a35f7408","tid":1606143,"uid":328320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"有冇建築物提議"},{"pid":"92637c5f8d1d79a3a048a59bf6678579c4ff0e5d","tid":1606143,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe63a3990808da504db65839565ce740a35f7408","tid":1606143,"uid":328320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"有冇建築物提議"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"10月1日 五區革命 整合版<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eeFrdT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eeFrdT</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個post漏咗各區政府合署"},{"pid":"a28be207ea834331d0da25757adc8924408c7b83","tid":1606143,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99acd5d10571f1eeff9b591bcc9a63f0444fe61c","tid":1606143,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"推"}]}